zornmesh trace
Reconstruct conversation timelines by correlation ID.

Usage: zornmesh trace <CORRELATION_ID> [OPTIONS]
       zornmesh trace events

Commands:
  events  Emit trace event stream scaffolding
  help    Print trace help

Options:
      --evidence <PATH>  Read this evidence log
      --span-tree        Include parent/child span reconstruction
      --output <FORMAT>  Select human or json output
  -h, --help  Print help
